Package: dynasimR
Type: Package
Title: Dynamic Agent-Node Simulation Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-04-15
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given   = "Raban A.",
      family  = "Heller",
      role    = c("aut", "cre"),
      email   = "r-heller@example.org"
    )
  )
Description:
    A domain-neutral framework for analysis and visualisation of
    discrete-event, agent-based and node-actor simulation outputs.
    Designed as a general-purpose toolkit for systems in which entities
    (actors, nodes, agents) move through states and interact within
    spatial or network environments. Supports two interchangeable
    output schemas (Profile A and Profile B) that can be analysed with
    a single API. Includes an interactive Shiny dashboard and
    publication-ready export helpers.
